data.value: To start, first set your directories. After this, restart your app to fully install these changes. then yout can drag and drop your files only on the panel. the number of files draged will always be hown on the panel. then press any action button either send, cloud copy or copy. This action will be done if your directories are well set. If you wish to know how and where each transfer was done, go to view history. and there, you will have much details about your transfers. If any problem or bugg is discovered please inform me using my contact.
